@{
    Layout = null;
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="az">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Meeting Not Found</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #022c22;
            color: #f8fafc;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(0, 255, 135, 0.05), transparent 60%);
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px 40px;
            background: rgba(6, 78, 59, 0.4);
            backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(0, 255, 135, 0.2);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 255, 135, 0.1);
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 90%;
            animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out;
        }
        @@keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); box-shadow: 0 0 0 rgba(0,0,0,0); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        .icon-container {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 24px auto;
            border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
        }
        .icon {
            font-size: 40px;
            color: #ef4444;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 26px;
            margin: 0 0 12px 0;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }
        p {
            color: #a7f3d0;
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0 0 32px 0;
        }
        .btn-back {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            background: rgba(0, 255, 135, 0.1);
            color: #00ff87;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            border: 1px solid #00ff87;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 255, 135, 0.2);
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .btn-back:hover {
            background: rgba(0, 255, 135, 0.2);
            color: white;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(0, 255, 135, 0.4);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="icon-container">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-link-slash icon"></i>
        </div>
        <h1>Sessiya Tap?lmad?</h1>
        <p>Qo?ulma?a çal??d???n?z Canl? D?rs mövcud deyil, vaxt? bitib v? ya art?q l??v edilib. Z?hm?t olmasa linki qrupdan yenid?n yoxlay?n.</p>
        <a href="/Course" class="btn-back"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left"></i> Kurslara Qay?t</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
